Title: S5 Ep. 204 JJ Walcutt PhD
Description:
Dr. JJ Walcutt is a must listen to podcast.  Who is she? A futurist, author, ran for president, research scientist, expert in training & learning, and a mom.  Sharing the same beliefs that life skills are valuable and relate to the working world, you will laugh and learn all in the hour we spend together.  Tune in and learn more about her.
